Interface FloatReceivePort

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, Port<java.lang.Float>, PortAutoCloseable, ReceivePort<java.lang.Float>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    FloatChannel
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    QueueFloatChannel, TickerChannelConsumer.TickerChannelFloatConsumer
    public interface FloatReceivePort
extends ReceivePort<java.lang.Float>
    A primitive float channel's consumer-side interface. All methods of this interface must only be called by the channel's owner.
